OL,3,CAlarm raised over number of people
OL,4,Cliving in tents on town's streets
OL,6,FA public meeting is to take place in
OL,7,FReading on Saturday 21 February to
OL,8,Fdiscuss how to tackle homelessness in
OL,9,Fthe town.
OL,11,FA rise in the number of tents pitched
OL,12,Fin car parks and open spaces has
OL,13,Ftriggered calls for action amid
OL,14,Fconcerns over safety and support for
OL,15,Frough sleepers.
OL,17,FFigures show the number of people
OL,18,Fsleeping on Reading's streets has
OL,19,Falmost doubled in the last few years
OL,20,Ffrom 22 in 2021, to at least 42 in
OL,21,F2024.
