OL,6,FThe meeting has been organised by
OL,7,FGrace Gomez, from The Way Ministry,
OL,8,Fand it comes after a 47-year-old man,
OL,9,Ffrom Kenya, froze to death while
OL,10,Fliving in a tent near the town centre.
OL,12,FMs Gomez said: "We need to have
OL,13,Fsomewhere safe for those people who
OL,14,Fare not considered a (housing)
OL,15,Fpriority so they can be safe at night,
OL,16,Fwhether it be one night, two nights,
OL,17,Fthree weeks until they can get
OL,18,Fthemselves back on their feet and get
OL,19,Fback into work.
