OL,6,F"I think something needs to be done
OL,7,Fbecause people have been homeless for
OL,8,Fa very long time in Reading.
OL,10,F"We recently lost somebody who froze
OL,11,Fto death is his tent. So I think we
OL,12,Fneed to come together, we need to take
OL,13,Faction.
OL,15,F"We need a permanent night shelter in
OL,16,Fthe town."
OL,18,FIn response to the death of Kepha
OL,19,FOtundo, Reading Borough Council said
OL,20,Fhe was offered support and a bed.
